00:04:26.570 --> 00:04:30.590
Whatever inside of us makes us go against the smart choice.

00:04:30.610 --> 00:04:34.630
(laughter) For whatever reason we have to do this and we have to continue doing this.

00:04:34.650 --> 00:04:38.680
You could be an outstanding artist and if no one ever knows you

00:04:38.700 --> 00:04:42.730
Or knows to talk to you. Or you never get the opportunity to

00:04:42.750 --> 00:04:46.780
invite them to see what you do on a personal level,

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:50.890
then you may never be discovered.

00:04:50.910 --> 00:04:55.010
But not everyone recognizes that chance. Or they don't do the things that are necessary to

00:04:55.030 --> 00:04:59.040
capitalize on their chance. And they may end up living the rest of their life

00:04:59.060 --> 00:05:03.090
and dying and not even knowing that, that was their chance.

00:05:03.110 --> 00:05:07.200
Because it was something small or mediocre or

00:05:07.220 --> 00:05:11.230
